Are the npc's also garbage collected on scene changes? If so I could change this:
@Subscribe
public void onGameStateChanged(GameStateChanged event)
{
  switch (event.getGameState())
  {
    case LOGIN_SCREEN:
    case HOPPING:
    case LOADING:
      reset();
      break;
    case LOGGED_IN:
      inDriftNetArea = checkArea();
      updateDriftNetVarbits();
      break;
  }
}

to
@Subscribe
public void onGameStateChanged(GameStateChanged event)
{
  if (event.getGameState() == LOGGED_IN) {
    inDriftNetArea = checkArea();
    updateDriftNetVarbits();
  }else {
    reset();
  }
}

And add annette = null to the reset function.

